abstract: Data will include the July unemployment report and personal income and spending for June, and companies reporting earnings will include Chrysler, General Motors and Toyota.
snippet: Data will include the July unemployment report and personal income and spending for June, and companies reporting earnings will include Chrysler, General Motors and Toyota.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS The data will include personal income and spending for June, the Standard & Poor’s/Case-Shiller home price index for May and consumer confidence for July (Tuesday); A.D.P. employment for July, the I.S.M. manufacturing index for July and construction spending for June (Wednesday); weekly jobless claims and factory orders for June (Thursday); and unemployment for July and the I.S.M. service index for July (Friday).

headline.main: Economic Reports for the Week Ahead
